# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:12
translate portuguese english2_ed786fbf:

    # "At the beginning of the class, Mrs. McGee starts walking around the room, passing out the graded quizzes that we had taken last week."
    "No início da aula, a Sra. McGee começa a andar pela sala, distribuindo os testes corrigidos que fizemos na semana passada."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:15
translate portuguese english2_731731ef:

    # "When she approaches my desk, she says my name."
    "Quando se aproxima da minha secretária, diz o meu nome."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:16
translate portuguese english2_952b41a4:

    # et "[pcname]."
    et "[pcname]."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:17
translate portuguese english2_844a3a46:

    # "She puts the graded quiz down on my desk."
    "Coloca o teste corrigido na minha secretária."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:18
translate portuguese english2_6711b135:

    # "An A is marked at the top of it."
    "Há um A marcado no topo."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:19
translate portuguese english2_2f82f17f:

    # "Perfect! I aced it."
    "Perfeito! Tirei nota máxima."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:21
translate portuguese english2_96a25b02:

    # "Mrs. McGee leans over in front of me. I can see her breasts shift around underneath her dress as she leans over."
    "A Sra. McGee inclina-se à minha frente. Consigo ver os seios dela a mexerem-se por baixo do vestido enquanto se inclina."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:22
translate portuguese english2_54e1945a:

    # "Part of me just wants to reach out and grab them."
    "Parte de mim só quer esticar o braço e agarrá-los."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:23
translate portuguese english2_b8ddb40c:

    # et "Great job, [pcname]. Best grade in the class."
    et "Excelente trabalho, [pcname]. A melhor nota da turma."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:24
translate portuguese english2_248280db:

    # et "Keep it up."
    et "Continua assim."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:29
translate portuguese english2_e99dc4e7:

    # "When she walks away, I notice Juliana looking over at me."
    "Quando ela se afasta, reparo que a Juliana está a olhar para mim."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:31
translate portuguese english2_14552a74:

    # "When she walks away, I notice the girl sitting near me looking over. Juliana, I think her name is."
    "Quando ela se afasta, reparo que a rapariga sentada ao meu lado está a olhar. Juliana, acho que é esse o nome dela."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:32
translate portuguese english2_27e7f98d:

    # "I can't tell if she is impressed, or jealous, or annoyed."
    "Não consigo perceber se ela está impressionada, com inveja ou irritada."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:33
translate portuguese english2_650a4a33:

    # "I notice that her quiz has an A at the top as well, but it is followed by a minus."
    "Reparo que o teste dela também tem um A no topo, mas seguido de um menos."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:34
translate portuguese english2_2c10dc66:

    # "Just barely less than mine."
    "Apenas um pouco abaixo do meu."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:36
translate portuguese english2_c3bd087a:

    # "After the quizzes are all passed out, Mrs. McGee goes over the answers on them, then we move on with our normal class."
    "Depois de distribuídos todos os testes, a Sra. McGee revê as respostas e, em seguida, continuamos com a aula normal."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:37
translate portuguese english2_2e9ad06e:

    # "Nothing else interesting happens in my other classes throughout the day. Just seemingly endless monotonous studying."
    "Nada de interessante acontece nas minhas outras aulas ao longo do dia. Apenas um estudo monótono que parece interminável."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:38
translate portuguese english2_231b2b98:

    # "Then, when my brain is just about mush, it's time to go to work."
    "Então, quando o meu cérebro está quase a derreter, é hora de ir trabalhar."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:2
    old "You have finished your English Homework"
    new "Terminaste o teu trabalho de casa de Inglês"

    # game/Scenes/School/English/english2.rpy:3
    old "Mrs. McGee will notice you the next time in her class."
    new "A Sra. McGee vai reparar em ti na próxima aula."

